==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ὅπλον / hoplon / hop'-lon

===Etymology===
*Probably from the primary word [[ἕπω]] hepō(to be busy about); an implement or utensil or tool (literally or figuratively, especially offensive for war): 

===Noun===
'''ὅπλον'''

# [[armour]], [[instrument]], [[weapon]].

